instructions: Put the plate on the charger
Put the napkin vertically in the center of the plate
Put the dinner fork vertically to the left of the charger
Put the salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
Put the dinner knife to the right of the charger, pointing up
Put the teaspoon to the right of the dinner knife head up
put the soup spoon to the right of the tea spoon head up
Put the water glass on the table above the tip of the dinner knife
Put the wine glass to the right of the water glass
Put the second wine glass below the first wine glass
Put the coffee cup to the right of the second wine glass
Put the bread plate on the table above the forks
Put the butter knife horizontally on the bread plate pointing toward the water glass
Put the dessert fork between the bread plate and the water glass, pointing toward the water glass
Put the dessert spoon between the charger and the dessert fork, pointing toward the bread plate
